Targeting S+ (version 31 and above) requires that one of FLAG_IMMUTABLE or FLAG_MUTABLE be specified when creating a PendingIntent.&lt;br&gt;
You need to change your code as below:
```
 reView = new RemoteViews(getPackageName(), R.layout.notify);
        Intent sendNotify = new Intent(this, Text.class);
        sendNotify.setAction(Fixed.ACTION.BASIC_ACT);
        sendNotify.setFlags(Intent.FLAG_ACTIVITY_SINGLE_TOP
                | Intent.FLAG_ACTIVITY_CLEAR_TOP);
        during = PendingIntent.getActivity(this, 0, sendNotify,
                Build.VERSION.SDK_INT &gt;= 23 ? PendingIntent.FLAG_IMMUTABLE : PendingIntent.FLAG_UPDATE_CURRENT);
        Intent sendPlay = new Intent(this, Notify.class);
        sendPlay.setAction(Fixed.ACTION.PLAY_ACT);
        PendingIntent pendingPlayIntent = PendingIntent.getService(this, 0,
                sendPlay, Build.VERSION.SDK_INT &gt;= 23 ? PendingIntent.FLAG_IMMUTABLE : PendingIntent.FLAG_UPDATE_CURRENT);
        reView.setOnClickPendingIntent(R.id.togglePlay, pendingPlayIntent);
```
Reference:&lt;br&gt;
https://developer.android.com/reference/android/app/PendingIntent

